= IMG_SaveJPG_RW =

Save a SDL_Surface into a JPEG image file.

== Syntax ==

<syntaxhighlight lang='c'>
int IMG_SaveJPG_RW(SDL_Surface *surface, SDL_RWops *dst, int freedst, int quality);
</syntaxhighlight>

== Function Parameters ==

{|
|'''surface'''
|SDL surface to save
|-
|'''dst'''
|RWops
|-
|'''freedst'''
|free dst
|-
|'''quality'''
|[0; 33] is Lowest quality, [34; 66] is Middle quality, [67; 100] is Highest quality
|}

== Return Value ==

Returns 0 if successful, -1 on error

